title: Auto Rim Shop - New Reconditioned 20" OEM Wheel for Mazda CX-9, 2011, 2012, 2013
features: This is a 20" Newly Reconditioned OEM Wheel for a 2011-2013 Mazda CX-9.
The Auto Rim Shop is the nation's leader for best-in-class rims and wheels. We provide several replica and OEM rim styles including Acura, Volkswagen, Chrysler, Ford, Lexus, BMW, and Nissan wheels.

description: This Factory OEM Mazda rim comes equipped on a 2011-2013 Mazda CX-9. This is an aluminum wheel with a diameter of 20" and a width of 7.5". This Mazda CX-9 wheel has 5 lug holes and a bolt pattern of 114.3mm. The offset of this Mazda CX-9 rim is 45mm. The corresponding OEM part number for this rim is Mazda part number(s): K52539965027500; 9965057500; 9965047500. The silver finish on this wheel has been refinished to brand new condition. This Mazda wheel is definitely the right wheel to get your 2011-2013 CX-9 on the road in style. This Mazda CX-9 wheel is a Factory OEM wheel. The wheel has been professionally refinished to like new condition in both quality and performance, making it a perfect match to your Mazda stock rims. All of our wheels are remanufactured to meet or exceed SAE and ASTM wheel testing standards. This ensures that not only does the wheel look like a new wheel off the Mazda assembly line, but it performs like one too. All of our Factory OEM wheels are backed by our Auto Rim Shop guarantee. Our guarantee ensures you receive the best possible quality wheel. If you are not 100% satisfied with your purchase, we will be happy to accept a return on your Mazda wheel in unused condition within 30 days of delivery. Please just let our customer service center know and we will be happy to make things right.
